<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101821722390421></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101821722390421><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=2336&mid=101821722390421>Got Lucky!!!</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=2336&mid=101821722390421#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=138371><span id= >bondiskey</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>3 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Apr 7th 6:11 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I finished this quest a couple days ago...and it took me about 15 minutes total to complete.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>I went to Qeynos first and tracked Moodoro...gave him 2gp and got the book...gave him 4gp and on second try I got the Jester...gave it back and got the page. <br>I immediately ported to WC and ran to HP...since it was my first time there I figured I'd just find the smugglers area.  I threw up track and couldn't believe that Dyllin Starshine was up after all I read I thought it would be hours.  No one was camping so I waited til no smugglers were around and root/nuke...only hitch was a smuggler joined in and I had to loot and run...jumped from cliff and gated.<br>Testament was more than worth the little effort I had to put in...Thank you to all that posted here!<br><br>Uuvien 29th Season Wood Elf Druid of Tunare<br>The Rathe Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
